title: From Childhood Traumas to Social Media Fame
description:
Before we look forward, we must look towards the past. This week, Tasia and Camo run through their troubled upbringings, all the run-ins with the law (and guns), and family issues. Tasia breaks down how she dropped out of high school, landed a few drug charges and got stuck in a really toxic relationship. Camo talks about some terrifying encounters with firearms, a family that didn’t understand them, and admits to a sexual assault at a very young age.
But it's not all bad news, they also talk about how they've learned from their past and how they built themselves up to the superstars they are today.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
